Rosina Ntshetsana Komane bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa bụ onye bụ onye omeiwu (MP) na National Assembly of South Africa kemgbe Mee, na afọ 2019. Komane bụ onye otu Economic Freedom Fighters.

N'ọnwa Juun afọ 2019, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye nnọchi anya Kọmitii Na-ahụ Maka Nkwado. Ọ ghọrọ onye nnọchi anya Kọmitii Portfolio na Public Enterprises na 6 Mee, na afọ 2020. A họpụtara Komane na Kọmitii Portfolio na Public Service and Administration, Performance Monitoring & Evaluation na 4 Septemba, na afọ 2020.
